#: {{usex|He changed his '''mind''' after hearing the speech.|lang=en}}
# Desire, inclination, or intention.
#: {{usex|She had a '''mind''' to go to Paris.|lang=en}}
#: {{usex|A '''mind''' to the madness.|lang=en}}
# A healthy mental state.
#: {{usex|I, ______ being of sound '''mind''' and body, do hereby ...|lang=en}}
#: {{usex|You are losing your '''mind'''.|lang=en}}
